title: Phantom Orchard Orchestra 2012 Trouble In Paradise
description: Phantom Orchard Orchestra ~ Trouble In Paradise ~ 2012 Tzadik Records TZ 7728. http://i5.imageban.ru/out/2017/08/19/9525ec9e89c62d1f5d27333d387612a9.jpg 1 Over The Gap 9:28 2 Red Blue And Green 10:22 3 Sun Metal 6:43 4 Face 11:19 5 Inner Reflection 4:14 6 House For 7 4:05 7 Laughter In The Dark 6:42 8 Trap 5:49 Maggie Parkins: cello Ikue Mori: electronics Hild Sofie Tafjord: french horn, electronics Zeena Parkins: electric & acoustic harps Shayna Dunkelman: percussion Sara Parkins: violin Maja Solveig Kjelstrup Ratkje: voice, electronics Members of bands as diverse as DNA, Skeleton Crew, Electric Masada, Hemophiliac and Björk, Zeena and Ikue have been leading figures of the downtown scene since the early 1980s. Their fabulous duo project Phantom Orchard is expanded here with five of the most exciting and creative women working in experimental music today. Created in 2008 for a project organized by the SWR radio in Baden Baden, the music has plenty of mystery, an exotic beauty and an orchestral sweep. This is experimental music at its very best. - Wayside Music
